node.text:
In 1979 a gruesome set of murders created a curse. Now, the life altering sins of the past revisits this small town 40 years later with a new string of murders.

Available now on iTunes and On Demand!
Check out our story for swipe up to watch 

With actors: @kanehodderkills #michaelberryman @undertheseascout  #briananthonywilson #tonydevon #michaelemery #ad #room9movie #room9movie2021

node.text:
In 1979 a gruesome set of murders created a curse. Now, the life altering sins of the past revisits this small town 40 years later with a new string of murders.

Available now on iTunes and On Demand!
Check out our story for swipe up to watch 

With actors: @kanehodderkills #michaelberryman @undertheseascout  #briananthonywilson #tonydevon #michaelemery #ad #room9movie #room9movie2021
